4
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:41,759
<i>Episode 16</i>

5
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,479
Starting today,

6
00:01:44,559 --> 00:01:46,679
you're just a slave in the Eagle Army.

7
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,679
What do you want me to do?

8
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,959
I want you to disappear from Tang.

9
00:01:58,759 --> 00:02:00,800
I have the final say in deciding whether I'm dead or not.

10
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,440
What you say is useless.

11
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,520
That depends on your capability.

12
00:02:06,199 --> 00:02:07,600
Keeping me by your side...

13
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:09,640
is like raising a tiger.

14
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:11,160
It makes no difference.

15
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,319
Make sure you survive first...

16
00:02:12,319 --> 00:02:13,559
before you are worried about that.

17
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,720
The law of survival on the grasslands...

18
00:02:17,639 --> 00:02:19,280
is only the strongest survives.

19
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:59,000
Behind me...

20
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,840
is Shuozhuo...

21
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:04,519
that has been looted but the people escaped the battle unscathed.

22
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:07,199
Behind it...

23
00:03:08,359 --> 00:03:10,000
is endless mountains.

24
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,600
Beyond that...

25
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:15,919
is my homeland, a million miles away.

26
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:18,840
Chang'an.

27
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:21,560
In the end, I couldn't go back there.

28
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,560
In the past, you achieved glory for the motherland.

29
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,960
Now, you're just a slave.

30
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:35,880
Li Chang Ge.

31
00:03:36,799 --> 00:03:38,720
Even I feel bad for you.

32
00:03:43,359 --> 00:03:45,079
<i>Fuju Inn</i>

33
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:46,199
After receiving the order,

34
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:47,519
I hurried here right away.

35
00:03:47,519 --> 00:03:48,519
Please give me your instructions, Commander Hao.

36
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,799
Follow Ashina Tribe at once.

37
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:53,120
I want to know what happened to Li Chang Ge in the end.

38
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,160
Should I kill her?

39
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:57,120
If she colludes with Ashina Tribe,

40
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:59,239
kill her.

41
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:01,400
What if she doesn't?

42
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:03,280
Ashina Tribe won't keep her.

43
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,039
Yes.

44
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,720
Send whatever news you have...

45
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:08,759
through the pigeon.

46
00:04:09,799 --> 00:04:10,799
You may leave.

47
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,199
Yes.

48
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:20,919
The people dearest to me...

49
00:04:21,039 --> 00:04:23,160
were all slaughtered like pigs and dogs.

50
00:04:23,770 --> 00:04:25,400
The place I was born and raised...

51
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,080
banished me.

52
00:04:27,239 --> 00:04:29,039
I felt like dying every single day.

53
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:32,210
But I had to do what I had to do.

54
00:04:33,799 --> 00:04:35,330
Once this is over,

55
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:37,799
it won't be too late to kill me.

56
00:04:37,919 --> 00:04:40,960
<i>Noble and integrate</i>

57
00:04:41,359 --> 00:04:42,559
Li Chang Ge.

58
00:04:43,210 --> 00:04:45,330
I hope you can sacrifice for the people.

59
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,239
Recently,

60
00:04:51,559 --> 00:04:52,879
all the county offices around the kingdom...

61
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:55,160
are secretly looking for the princess.

62
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:57,770
However, the portrait that was sent to the capital...

63
00:04:57,879 --> 00:05:00,080
looks nothing like the princess.

64
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:03,239
Furthermore, the princess lost in the four states in the north.

65
00:05:03,239 --> 00:05:04,239
Until now,

66
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:07,600
we haven't heard anything yet.

67
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,400
Your Highness.

68
00:05:10,119 --> 00:05:12,840
Princess Yong'an is very blessed.

69
00:05:13,919 --> 00:05:15,919
Didn't Li Chun Feng make a prediction...

70
00:05:15,919 --> 00:05:18,239
that she'll come back safely?

71
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,960
I hope so.

72
00:05:22,039 --> 00:05:23,280
Lately,

73
00:05:24,559 --> 00:05:25,650
I always dreamed of...

74
00:05:25,650 --> 00:05:27,999
Le Yan and Chang Ge when they were younger.

75
00:05:29,799 --> 00:05:30,840
Both of them...

76
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:32,999
were hanging around in the garden.

77
00:05:33,919 --> 00:05:35,200
I waved at them...

78
00:05:35,879 --> 00:05:37,239
but they couldn't see me.

79
00:05:37,799 --> 00:05:39,520
I called out their names.

80
00:05:39,919 --> 00:05:41,280
But they couldn't hear me either.

81
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,919
Worse,

82
00:05:43,039 --> 00:05:44,559
they kept running away.

83
00:05:49,239 --> 00:05:50,640
Your Highness...

84
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:52,119
worries too much.

85
00:05:52,119 --> 00:05:53,160
That's why...

86
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:55,600
Your Highness had weird dreams.

87
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:58,679
Your Highness, I'll get the imperial kitchen...

88
00:05:58,679 --> 00:06:01,879
to make some soothing soup for Your Highness.

89
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,799
Will those two girls...

90
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:07,200
be further away from me?

91
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,080
No.

92
00:06:09,919 --> 00:06:12,520
They will always be...

93
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:14,080
the most daring daughter and official to you.

94
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:21,080
Perhaps at this moment,

95
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,439
no news is the best news.

96
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:25,160
That's right.

97
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:30,400
Your Highness, there is urgent military news.

98
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:32,400
Ashina Tribe suddenly attacked the north border.

99
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:34,679
The chief commander, Sima Tu...

100
00:06:34,679 --> 00:06:36,720
and the governor of Shuozhou, Gongsun Heng...

101
00:06:37,119 --> 00:06:38,320
were killed in the battle.

102
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:40,160
When did it happen?

103
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,799
No one reported it!

104
00:06:41,799 --> 00:06:43,600
Ashina Tribe besieged the city.

105
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:46,080
The frontier couldn't deliver the message.

106
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:49,160
Hao Du sent his men to speed things up.

107
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,760
Five horses were sacrificed...

108
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:52,760
before the news reached Chang'an.

109
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,960
Send our army there now to regain the north region.

110
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:58,520
Make sure we chase the Ashina Tribe out of the border.

111
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:00,039
After that,

112
00:07:00,039 --> 00:07:01,479
the troops will camp at the same place...

113
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,840
to comfort the people in the north.

114
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:05,039
Yes, Your Highness.

115
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,600
Mr. Du.

116
00:07:11,439 --> 00:07:12,439
Mr. Du.

117
00:07:12,799 --> 00:07:15,760
I need to talk to you.

118
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:20,840
You always know your own mind.

119
00:07:21,479 --> 00:07:23,039
What do you want to discuss with me?

120
00:07:23,039 --> 00:07:25,400
Mr. Du, don't be sarcastic.

121
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:27,400
You and I are the ministers of the imperial court.

122
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:29,799
It's good to have someone to discuss with.

123
00:07:29,919 --> 00:07:31,239
Furthermore,

124
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:33,439
I really need a favor from you.

125
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,200
Just tell me what it is.

126
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:37,960
As you know,

127
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,720
Princess Yong'an is missing in action.

128
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:42,080
It's His Highness's biggest concern.

129
00:07:42,439 --> 00:07:43,520
The portrait of Princess Yong'an...

130
00:07:43,520 --> 00:07:45,119
has been sent to all local government offices...

131
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,679
for a secret investigation.

132
00:07:46,679 --> 00:07:47,799
However, Princess Yong'an is nowhere to be found.

133
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,600
But we didn't receive any news...

134
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,359
from the north.

135
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,160
I'm just worried.

136
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:57,119
What do you want me to do?

137
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,799
People in the north...

138
00:07:58,799 --> 00:08:01,160
have never seen Princess Yong'an before.

139
00:08:01,679 --> 00:08:04,760
Your godson is in the north, right?

140
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,760
Although Wei Shu Yu...

141
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:09,799
allegedly lost her,

142
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,400
at that time,

143
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,679
your godson, Hao Du...

144
00:08:12,799 --> 00:08:14,919
was with Princess Yong'an.

145
00:08:14,919 --> 00:08:16,280
The more collaborative the effort,

146
00:08:16,999 --> 00:08:18,039
the better.

147
00:08:18,239 --> 00:08:20,520
Furthermore, under your guidance,

148
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:22,520
- your godson is already... - That's enough.

149
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,359
Talk properly.

150
00:08:24,359 --> 00:08:25,359
Don't flatter me.

151
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,640
Since His Highness...

152
00:08:27,799 --> 00:08:29,999
has entrusted you with this case,

153
00:08:30,479 --> 00:08:31,799
you should work on it.

154
00:08:38,519 --> 00:08:39,600
Yes.

155
00:08:40,810 --> 00:08:41,810
Eat up.

156
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,239
Here.

157
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:47,159
What's the point of keeping him here?

158
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:49,359
If you ask me, I'll just kill him.

159
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,600
- Hold on. - Here.

160
00:08:51,999 --> 00:08:53,050
Leave it there.

161
00:08:54,879 --> 00:08:56,050
Give me more.

162
00:08:56,359 --> 00:08:57,359
Here.

163
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,879
Where are you going?

164
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,279
I didn't expect to see you here.

165
00:09:12,279 --> 00:09:13,320
Here.

166
00:09:17,050 --> 00:09:18,239
Actually, the Eagle Army...

167
00:09:18,359 --> 00:09:19,600
isn't too far from Shuozhou.

168
00:09:20,159 --> 00:09:21,690
It's near a river and there are trees.

169
00:09:21,690 --> 00:09:22,930
You'll get used to it.

170
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:24,999
Eat up.

171
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,690
Let me tell you.

172
00:09:28,690 --> 00:09:30,159
If His Highness didn't care about you,

173
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,639
I wouldn't care about you either.

174
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:33,560
My goodness.

175
00:09:37,810 --> 00:09:40,119
Your friend is insensible.

176
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:43,080
I think you're wasting your effort on him.

177
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,810
Look at that body.

178
00:09:44,999 --> 00:09:46,960
I don't think he can survive in the grasslands.

179
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,320
No, he'll survive.

180
00:09:48,519 --> 00:09:49,560
How do you know that?

181
00:09:50,119 --> 00:09:52,050
He is someone who has a strong desire to live.

182
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,440
He won't be defeated...

183
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:58,320
so easily.

184
00:09:58,810 --> 00:10:00,119
It looks like...

185
00:10:00,119 --> 00:10:01,639
you know him very well.

186
00:10:02,119 --> 00:10:03,200
But I think...

187
00:10:03,359 --> 00:10:05,440
you're just the enemy to him.

188
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:07,930
It doesn't matter.

189
00:10:10,479 --> 00:10:12,930
You've never treated me so nicely after all these years.

190
00:10:29,999 --> 00:10:30,999
That person...

191
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:32,399
has been following us for a long time.

192
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,479
I know.

193
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,119
He's here to see Shi Si Lang.

194
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,479
Do something for me.

195
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,239
What are you doing?

196
00:10:45,359 --> 00:10:46,399
Let go!

197
00:10:46,879 --> 00:10:47,960
Listen to me.

198
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,519
You're our slave.

199
00:10:49,519 --> 00:10:51,080
Just do whatever I tell you to do.

200
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:52,600
What?

201
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,159
Are you refusing to work?

202
00:10:54,690 --> 00:10:56,239
You must have a death wish.

203
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:58,239
Take him away.

204
00:10:58,399 --> 00:10:59,440
Cut him into pieces and feed him to the dogs!

205
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:00,600
- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.

206
00:11:02,639 --> 00:11:03,720
What are you doing?

207
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,800
What are you doing?

208
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:05,999
Let go of me!

209
00:11:06,759 --> 00:11:07,800
Let go!

210
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,359
Come on!

211
00:11:09,359 --> 00:11:10,440
Let go!

212
00:11:13,479 --> 00:11:14,479
Come on!

213
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,320
Elder Qin.

214
00:11:51,639 --> 00:11:53,359
I feel bad for Yuan Niang.

215
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,320
She has been homeless and travels with us for so long.

216
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,239
Not at all.

217
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:02,159
She has the best father and mother in the world.

218
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:05,920
How is Shuozhou doing?

219
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,600
I heard that...

220
00:12:08,759 --> 00:12:10,200
the Ashina Tribe has left.

221
00:12:10,759 --> 00:12:13,040
Someone from the imperial court will come and take over the rest.

222
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,359
Aside from that...

223
00:12:16,999 --> 00:12:18,159
"Aside from that"?

224
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,519
Are you going to tell me...

225
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:21,200
about Young Master?

226
00:12:22,519 --> 00:12:24,479
He failed in the assassination.

227
00:12:24,479 --> 00:12:25,479
He was killed.

228
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,800
I see. He's...

229
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,759
He's too strong and impulsive.

230
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:33,119
It's easy to destroy those who are strong and impulsive.

231
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:34,920
If...

232
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:38,920
Stop it.

233
00:12:39,279 --> 00:12:40,600
I think Young Master...

234
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:42,279
is still alive.

235
00:12:42,639 --> 00:12:44,200
He's still alive?

236
00:12:44,519 --> 00:12:46,479
Since Ashina Sun...

237
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,680
made a promise with Governor Gongsun,

238
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:50,840
he won't kill him for sure.

239
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:54,080
Perhaps he has brought him to the grasslands.

240
00:12:54,479 --> 00:12:55,800
Let's not wait any longer.

241
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,759
- Let's look for him. - In the grasslands,

242
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:59,680
they have spies everywhere.

243
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:02,440
We can't barge in as we like.

244
00:13:04,359 --> 00:13:06,359
Let's take care of Yuan Niang first.

245
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:09,040
We should use our previous connection...

246
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:11,279
and see if we can get some information.

247
00:13:11,279 --> 00:13:12,359
Then I'll make a decision.

248
00:13:24,279 --> 00:13:27,560
<i>Someone has been executed by Ashina Sun.</i>

249
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,759
Li Chang Ge.

250
00:13:35,519 --> 00:13:37,279
Perhaps this is the best place for you.

251
00:13:55,639 --> 00:13:56,680
Why are you here?

252
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,759
That's my question for you.

253
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:01,440
Losing the princess is a serious matter...

254
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:03,359
yet His Highness didn't blame you.

255
00:14:03,879 --> 00:14:05,519
I'll find Le Yan for sure.

256
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:07,639
I'll wait and see.

257
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:10,119
It has been so long.

258
00:14:10,279 --> 00:14:11,399
You didn't return to Chang'an.

259
00:14:12,399 --> 00:14:13,639
Are you looking for Chang Ge?

260
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,080
What happened to her?

261
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:18,840
She's dead.

262
00:14:21,639 --> 00:14:22,800
How did she die?

263
00:14:24,359 --> 00:14:25,440
Did you kill her?

264
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:29,840
Tell me!

265
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,239
Wei Shu Yu.

266
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:44,639
Do you plan to sacrifice yourself and your family...

267
00:14:44,639 --> 00:14:46,639
just to avenge your lover?

268
00:14:46,759 --> 00:14:47,960
After killing you,

269
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:50,759
I'll kill myself to atone for it.

270
00:14:50,759 --> 00:14:52,600
Do you think that His Highness...

271
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:54,960
will punish the Wei family just for you?

272
00:14:57,359 --> 00:14:58,560
Then why didn't you do it?

273
00:14:59,879 --> 00:15:01,600
When Li Chang Ge was alive, you couldn't do anything.

274
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:02,639
Now that she's dead,

275
00:15:02,759 --> 00:15:03,840
you found the courage to take revenge.

276
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:06,879
I guess,

277
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:09,239
that's because you know that since Li Chang Ge is dead,

278
00:15:09,359 --> 00:15:11,479
your family's glory won't be affected.

279
00:15:19,479 --> 00:15:20,879
Even if you want revenge,

280
00:15:20,879 --> 00:15:21,999
you've come to the wrong person.

281
00:15:22,999 --> 00:15:24,279
I didn't kill Li Chang Ge.

