569
00:30:54,080 --> 00:30:55,560
You scared her.

570
00:30:55,919 --> 00:30:57,000
One cookie is three cents.

571
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,240
Don't think that it's expensive.

572
00:30:58,240 --> 00:30:59,280
The war is still going on.

573
00:30:59,480 --> 00:31:01,359
