592
00:32:04,159 --> 00:32:05,199
Hey.

593
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:18,639
I'm sorry.

594
00:32:18,639 --> 00:32:19,679
It's all right.

595
00:32:19,679 --> 00:32:21,719
