604
00:32:43,320 --> 00:32:45,000
You must be a fool.

605
00:32:46,600 --> 00:32:47,919
Come and take a look.

606
00:32:50,080 --> 00:32:51,080
My pouch.

607
00:32:51,600 --> 00:32:52,679
My pouch!

608
00:32:54,119 --> 00:32:55,280
Stop right there!

609
00:32:56,959 --> 00:32:58,000
Stop right there!

610
00:32:59,399 --> 00:33:01,159
My pouch!

611
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:04,320
Stop right there!

612
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:08,399
Stop right there!

613
00:33:19,919 --> 00:33:21,000
Stop right there!

614
00:33:23,040 --> 00:33:24,240
Give me back my pouch.

615
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:25,439
You can take the money.

616
00:33:43,639 --> 00:33:44,719
Right.

617
00:33:44,719 --> 00:33:45,879
Here. This is for you.

618
00:33:49,600 --> 00:33:51,159
It's so ugly. What's this?

619
00:33:51,159 --> 00:33:52,679
My hands got pricked in order to make that,

620
00:33:52,679 --> 00:33:53,800
and you're even complaining that it's ugly.

621
00:33:53,800 --> 00:33:56,399
- Forget it then. - It is ugly,

622
00:33:56,560 --> 00:33:57,919
but I like it.

623
00:34:01,320 --> 00:34:02,639
Chang Ge.

624
00:34:07,439 --> 00:34:08,719
Where are you?

625
00:34:21,480 --> 00:34:22,560
Have you seen the lady...

626
00:34:22,719 --> 00:34:23,719
on the portrait?

627
00:34:23,889 --> 00:34:24,889
No.

628
00:34:26,319 --> 00:34:27,369
Have you seen this lady?

629
00:34:27,369 --> 00:34:28,369
No.

630
00:34:29,639 --> 00:34:30,719
This lady in the portrait,

631
00:34:30,929 --> 00:34:32,000
have you seen her before?

632
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:33,000
No.

633
00:34:34,679 --> 00:34:36,409
