Why are you following me?

645
00:35:35,119 --> 00:35:36,199
They want to arrest me.

646
00:35:36,369 --> 00:35:37,759
What did you do?

647
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,279
I didn't do anything wrong.

648
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:41,159
They accused me of pretending to be the princess.

649
00:35:41,279 --> 00:35:43,279
Why did you do that?

650
00:35:43,759 --> 00:35:45,119
Young lady.

651
00:35:45,119 --> 00:35:46,719
Are you a fool?

652
00:35:46,929 --> 00:35:49,040
I'm not pretending to be a princess. I really...

653
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:57,000
Open the door!

654
00:35:58,319 --> 00:35:59,319
Open the door!

655
00:36:00,719 --> 00:36:01,759
Coming.

656
00:36:01,759 --> 00:36:03,040
Are you going to pay me if you break the door?

657
00:36:05,159 --> 00:36:06,279
It's still daytime.

658
00:36:06,279 --> 00:36:07,600
What's the rush?

659
00:36:07,799 --> 00:36:09,409
Are you here to buy clothes?

660
00:36:10,639 --> 00:36:11,929
We're chasing after a girl.

661
00:36:12,119 --> 00:36:13,679
I saw her walking on this street.

662
00:36:13,679 --> 00:36:14,679
Have you seen her before?

663
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:18,119
We're looking for her.

664
00:36:23,409 --> 00:36:24,560
Yes, I have.

665
00:36:25,929 --> 00:36:29,560
This lady was pickpocketed on the street earlier.

666
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:31,319
She went after the perpetrator, heading south.

667
00:36:32,369 --> 00:36:34,889
Sir, what did she do?

668
00:36:34,889 --> 00:36:36,719
Is she a robber?

669
00:36:36,839 --> 00:36:38,839
This area is not safe lately.

670
00:36:46,719 --> 00:36:48,159
- Search the place. - Hey!

671
00:36:48,159 --> 00:36:50,000
Sir!

672
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:07,889
<i>Great virtue brings happiness</i>

673
00:37:07,889 --> 00:37:09,000
What's the matter?

674
00:37:09,279 --> 00:37:11,480
- I don't know. - What's wrong?

675
00:37:30,040 --> 00:37:31,440
- We didn't find anything. - We didn't find anything.

676
00:37:32,639 --> 00:37:33,639
She's not there either.

677
00:37:34,639 --> 00:37:37,080
Sir, as I said, she's not here.

678
00:37:37,080 --> 00:37:39,279
My textile workshop is operating.

679
00:37:39,409 --> 00:37:41,799
You simply look around the workshop.

680
00:37:41,799 --> 00:37:43,239
It will leave a bad impression.

681
00:37:43,239 --> 00:37:44,279
That's enough.

682
00:37:44,639 --> 00:37:45,799
If you see her again,

683
00:37:45,799 --> 00:37:46,799
