684
00:37:47,199 --> 00:37:48,199
Of course.

685
00:37:49,239 --> 00:37:50,279
Let's go.

686
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:08,000
You're smart.

687
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:09,119
At least you hid in the tank.

688
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:11,159
Thank you for the help.

689
00:38:11,369 --> 00:38:13,159
I thought you wouldn't save me.

690
00:38:13,319 --> 00:38:14,319
That's enough.

691
00:38:14,480 --> 00:38:16,409
You don't seem like a bad person.

692
00:38:17,080 --> 00:38:18,960
They have nothing better to do.

693
00:38:19,119 --> 00:38:20,889
You're just pretending to be a princess.

694
00:38:21,080 --> 00:38:22,080
Do they really have to do that?

695
00:38:22,239 --> 00:38:23,319
Ma'am.

696
00:38:23,319 --> 00:38:24,520
I'm not pretending.

697
00:38:24,759 --> 00:38:26,239
I'm really a princess.

698
00:38:26,239 --> 00:38:27,369
All right.

699
00:38:27,369 --> 00:38:29,480
It doesn't matter if you're a princess or a lord.

700
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:30,480
I need to get back to work.

701
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:31,639
You should go.

702
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:33,040
Ma'am.

703
00:38:33,040 --> 00:38:35,000
If I go out right now,

704
00:38:35,119 --> 00:38:36,440
I'll get caught.

705
00:38:36,560 --> 00:38:37,639
I beg you.

706
00:38:37,639 --> 00:38:39,279
Please let me stay here for one more day.

707
00:38:39,409 --> 00:38:40,759
I beg you.

708
00:38:42,040 --> 00:38:43,239
All right.

709
00:38:43,369 --> 00:38:45,080
Go inside and get changed.

710
00:38:45,679 --> 00:38:47,369
Don't blame me when you get sick.

711
00:38:49,040 --> 00:38:50,409
Thank you, ma'am.

712
00:39:02,319 --> 00:39:03,889
So this is the grassland.

713
00:39:05,889 --> 00:39:07,480
It's so vast.

714
00:39:10,520 --> 00:39:11,639
Madam Su Yi Li.

715
00:39:11,639 --> 00:39:12,719
Do you have more cheese?

716
00:39:12,719 --> 00:39:14,639
- Please keep some for me. - Sure.

717
00:39:14,639 --> 00:39:16,040
Come to my tent later.

718
00:39:16,159 --> 00:39:17,239
You can have as much as you want.

719
00:39:18,239 --> 00:39:20,369
Your Highness, are there any presents for us?

720
00:39:20,719 --> 00:39:23,080
Ye, everyone gets a present.

721
00:39:23,520 --> 00:39:24,560
Ya Luo.

722
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:28,409
Your Highness, the herbs are ready.

723
00:39:28,409 --> 00:39:29,480
Here they are.

724
00:39:31,159 --> 00:39:32,199
Take a look.

725
00:39:33,159 --> 00:39:34,239
It's not bad.

726
00:39:36,279 --> 00:39:37,839
- Here, Your Highness. - Take a look.

727
00:39:38,040 --> 00:39:39,080
Help yourself.

728
00:39:39,279 --> 00:39:41,000
- There are presents! - I want this.

729
00:39:43,759 --> 00:39:44,759
This is good.

730
00:39:45,239 --> 00:39:46,319
- Look. - Let me see.

731
00:39:47,369 --> 00:39:49,279
Uncle Shi Min, where is my reward?

732
00:39:49,279 --> 00:39:50,409
- Where is my reward? - Where is my reward?

733
00:39:50,409 --> 00:39:51,929
- Stand still. - Where is my reward?

734
00:39:51,929 --> 00:39:53,040
Stand still and close your eyes.

735
00:39:53,409 --> 00:39:54,639
Close your eyes. Close them.

736
00:39:59,759 --> 00:40:01,319
What about me, Uncle Shi Min? Where's mine?

737
00:40:01,319 --> 00:40:02,679
- Give it to me - I only have one pony.

738
00:40:04,239 --> 00:40:06,480
- I'll give it if you can reach it. - Give it to me, Father!

739
00:40:07,080 --> 00:40:08,119
Give it to me.

740
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:13,000
Father!

741
00:40:17,799 --> 00:40:19,000
Uncle Shi Min!

742
00:40:19,159 --> 00:40:21,080
Father, don't go against your words.

743
00:40:21,080 --> 00:40:22,080
Father!

744
00:40:22,799 --> 00:40:23,889
Uncle Shi Min!

745
00:40:26,040 --> 00:40:27,520
Give it to me, Uncle Shi Min!

746
00:40:27,759 --> 00:40:28,889
You promised me!

747
00:40:36,119 --> 00:40:37,759
- Here, let me help you. - Thank you.

748
00:40:38,239 --> 00:40:39,279
Not bad.

749
00:40:39,600 --> 00:40:40,639
That was fun.

750
00:40:42,409 --> 00:40:43,440
Hey!

751
00:40:45,409 --> 00:40:46,799
You're good in Cuju, right?

752
00:40:47,560 --> 00:40:48,560
This is for you.

753
00:40:49,600 --> 00:40:51,639
Can we have the ball?

754
00:40:57,679 --> 00:40:58,679
Here.

755
00:41:00,719 --> 00:41:02,119
- Stop right there! - Come on!

756
00:41:02,119 --> 00:41:03,119
Wait for me!

757
00:41:04,520 --> 00:41:05,799
Slow down!

758
00:41:06,199 --> 00:41:07,600
- Give it to me. - No.

759
00:41:10,119 --> 00:41:11,440
I'll send the present home for them.

760
00:41:11,600 --> 00:41:13,080
- Hold it properly. - Can you take it to him?

761
00:41:27,929 --> 00:41:29,759
The pay is so low.

762
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:31,960
Madam Zhang, you should consider yourself lucky.

763
00:41:32,080 --> 00:41:33,520
At least we still have work to do.

764
00:41:33,520 --> 00:41:34,560
We won't be starving to death.

765
00:41:34,560 --> 00:41:35,639
That's not bad.

766
00:41:36,409 --> 00:41:37,440
You're right.

767
00:41:37,560 --> 00:41:39,159
It's getting difficult to use the machine.

768
00:41:39,279 --> 00:41:40,409
Yes.

769
00:41:48,440 --> 00:41:49,520
Madam Chai.

770
00:41:49,520 --> 00:41:51,119
You finally hired someone.

771
00:41:52,080 --> 00:41:53,119
I found her on the street.

772
00:41:53,119 --> 00:41:54,239
She'll leave tomorrow.

773
00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:02,040
Greetings, everyone.

774
00:42:03,679 --> 00:42:05,239
What are you looking at?

775
00:42:05,239 --> 00:42:06,239
Get back to work!

776
00:42:11,199 --> 00:42:13,040
She's so pretty.

777
00:42:14,080 --> 00:42:15,929
What kind of salutation was that?

778
00:42:15,929 --> 00:42:18,409
I don't know. It looks nice though.

779
00:42:18,409 --> 00:42:19,409
Exactly.

780
00:42:19,520 --> 00:42:20,929
Greetings, everyone.

781
00:42:20,929 --> 00:42:21,929
That's not correct.

782
00:42:21,929 --> 00:42:23,040
It's like this.

783
00:42:23,159 --> 00:42:25,159
- No. - That's what she did.

784
00:42:26,889 --> 00:42:28,480
You'll sleep here tonight.

785
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:30,279
You have to leave tomorrow.

786
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:31,889
I don't feed people for nothing.

787
00:42:32,440 --> 00:42:33,889
Thank you, ma'am.

788
00:42:33,889 --> 00:42:35,799
I will repay you someday.

789
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:37,199
Thank you.

790
00:42:47,040 --> 00:42:48,639
What should I do tomorrow?

791
00:42:49,239 --> 00:42:51,560
