794
00:43:01,960 --> 00:43:04,239
Please pardon me.

795
00:43:04,239 --> 00:43:05,369
Princess Yong'an...

796
00:43:05,369 --> 00:43:07,480
We lost her.

797
00:43:09,239 --> 00:43:11,000
It's fine if you can't find her.

798
00:43:11,159 --> 00:43:12,440
What do you mean you lost her?

799
00:43:12,440 --> 00:43:16,159
We saw a lady who looks like her on the street.

800
00:43:16,159 --> 00:43:19,080
But she got away.

801
00:43:19,080 --> 00:43:20,319
A lady who looks like her?

802
00:43:20,600 --> 00:43:21,679
How did she run away?

803
00:43:22,000 --> 00:43:24,440
Mr. Wei, we'll keep looking.

804
00:43:24,560 --> 00:43:27,759
However, Princess Yong'an has feet.

805
00:43:27,889 --> 00:43:29,440
We are unsure...

806
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:31,560
whether she's still in Yunzhou or not.

807
00:43:31,560 --> 00:43:33,000
How dare you absolve yourself?

808
00:43:33,199 --> 00:43:34,279
Yes.

809
00:43:34,279 --> 00:43:36,560
We'll keep looking.

810
00:43:37,600 --> 00:43:38,839
- I'll look for her tomorrow! - I'll look for her tomorrow!

811
00:43:39,119 --> 00:43:40,159
- Get lost! - Get lost!

812
00:43:40,159 --> 00:43:41,159
Yes, sir!

813
00:43:46,119 --> 00:43:47,199
Yan Er.

814
00:43:48,080 --> 00:43:49,159
Where are you?

